io.lettuce.core.protocol

接口 DemandAware


  • public interface DemandAware
    Interface for demand-aware components.

    A demand-aware component is aware of its demand for data that is read from the DemandAware.Source and possibly awaits processing. A DemandAware.Sink with demand is ready to process data. A DemandAware.Sink without demand signals that it's ability to keep up with the incoming data is no longer given and it wishes to receive no more data. Submitting more data could cause overload and exhaust buffer space.

    从以下版本开始:
    5.0

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明
      static interface  DemandAware.Sink
      A demand-aware DemandAware.Sink that accepts data.
      static interface  DemandAware.Source
      A DemandAware.Source provides data to a DemandAware and can be notified to produce more input for the command.
